> Point #11 On Kennedy's Intent to Withdraw From Vietnam
> =0D
> =46rom The Nation, 3/9/92, p. 319
> =0D
> Cockburn:
> =0D
> (After comparing two versions of NSAM 273, the order that
> reversed Kennedy's stated policy of withdrawal in NSAM 263:)
